Uses of Package
com.xatkit.intent

  • Packages that use com.xatkit.intent 
    Package Description
    com.xatkit.core
    Contains the core components of the Xatkit framework.
    com.xatkit.core.platform.io
    Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platform's input provider.
    com.xatkit.core.recognition
    Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom intent recognition.
    com.xatkit.core.recognition.dialogflow
    An intent recognition implementation for the DialogFlow platform.
    com.xatkit.core.session
    Contains the classes to manage sessions and contexts.
    com.xatkit.execution
    Contains the interfaces to manipulate Execution models.
    com.xatkit.execution.impl
    Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Execution models.
    com.xatkit.intent
    Contains the interfaces to manipulate Intent models.
    com.xatkit.intent.impl
    Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Intent models.
    com.xatkit.intent.util
    Contains utility classes used to manipulate Intent models.
    com.xatkit.platform
    Contains the interfaces to manipulate Platform models.
    com.xatkit.platform.impl
    Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Platform models.
    com.xatkit.plugins.chat.platform.io
